  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nIf User1 has a profile picture and setting `Show profile picture to - Contacts`, User2 has `Show profile picture from - None`, and User1 and User2 are contacts, but after that User2 changes the setting to `Show profile picture of - Everyone` (or `Contacts`), then this new option will not apply until User1 sends a message to a public chat.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. User1 has a default `Show profile picture to - Contacts`, sets a profile picture\r\n2. User2 changes the setting to `Show profile picture from - None`\r\n3. User1 adds User2 to contacts, User2 adds User1 to contacts\r\n4. User2 changes the setting to `Show profile picture from - Everyone`\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nUser2 can see the profile picture of User1 immediately after changing the setting\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nUser2 will not see updates from User1 until (1) he posts smth to the public chat to which both are joined OR (2) he will change his profile picture\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 11/10\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\ncc @cammellos ",
